        <abstract> 
<p>Continued discussion of Jamieson’s Glen Roy theory. Mentions river erosion of glaciers. Quotes from old letter to CL [<hi rend="doubleUnderline">1116</hi>].</p> 
            <p>Is working hard on orchids; fears subject is too complex for the public.</p>
